    "Sort Optimizations.",
    "As discussed before, by splitting the whole optimization task into small pieces, various optimizations can help each other.",
    "DeGPT achieves this by adequately arranging the order of the optimizations and letting the previous optimization provide additional information for the succeeding optimizations.",
    "Generally speaking, the optimizations mentioned above can be divided into two classes.",
    "One is the structure-related optimizations, which will change the abstract syntax tree of the code, such as removing the redundant variables."
